wiki.summary: "WAKE UP F1LTHY" (Previously known as "00CACTUS") is a song that was recorded by Playboi Carti and Travis Scott in 2022 for Playboi Carti's album "MUSIC", being track 17 on the project. The song was first previewed by popular streamer Adin Ross on July 12 2024, revealing that BNYX and F1LTHY both had production on the song. Exactly 1 month later, the full unfinished and unmastered song would surface as a 5k bonus from a 10k groupbuy. The song is also one of the two leaks that made it on the album, with the other being "MOJO JOJO". Read more on Last.fm.
